  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Kaya is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>You can fuel up for the day with a continental buffet breakfast which has a variety of locally sourced cheeses, charcuterie and condiments. There are also freshly prepared hot options available each day. Breakfast is served from 7.30-10.30am. </p>
<p>Enjoy à la carte evening meals where you have a choice of menu. Dishes are often prepared with local ingredients and have a French flare to them. Earlier meal times are available for children (on request).</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included </p>
<p>Special dietary requirements (vegetarian, gluten free etc.) are available on request. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
