  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Kaya has an ideal location in Les Menuires, with easy access to the slopes and a ten minute walk to the resort centre. After a day of exploring the mountain, the hotel has a wonderful wellness area with a heated indoor pool.</p>
<h2>Access to the Three Valleys</h2>
<p>The Kaya is a cosy spa hotel located in the Reberty area of <a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a>, which forms part of the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a> ski area. Within minutes of leaving the hotel, you can be skiing the 600km of fantastic varied pistes, then ski back to the door to soak up the last rays of sun from the large south-facing terrace with beautiful views. </p>
<h2>Cosy rooms</h2>
<div class="panel-content">
<p>Decorated in a contemporary Alpine style, the hotel offers you a cosy and comfortable place to stay during your holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>. Each room is generous in size and has all the facilities you need for a home away from home stay. Sit back and relax with fantastic views over the surrounding mountain peaks.</p>
<h2>Unwind and relax </h2>
</div>
<div id="tns4-ow" class="tns-outer">
<div id="tns4-mw" class="tns-ovh tns-ah">
<div id="tns4-iw" class="tns-inner">
<div id="tns4" class="itemCollection roomsWidget js-roomsWidget  tns-slider tns-carousel tns-subpixel tns-calc tns-horizontal">
<div id="tns4-item0" class="item tns-item" aria-hidden="true">
<div class="item-titleContainer">
<div class="item-subtitle">
<p>After a day on the slopes, soak away your achy muscles in the wellness area which has an indoor heated pool which has stunning views of the surrounding mountains, a sauna and steam room, as well as numerous available massage treatments. Alternatively, the bar and lounge area provides you with a warm and cosy atmosphere to enjoy a well deserved drink after a day of exploring the mountains. For the younger guests there is a children's area with a variety of toys, games and video games. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></description>
