  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Kaya is a superb hotel located in the Reberty area of Les Menuires, part of the world-renowned Three Valleys ski area. With its piste-side location and fabulous facilities, the hotel promises a winter holiday to remember. This hotel is offered on a half board basis and includes breakfast and dinner with your stay. </p>]]></listingDescription>
