  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p> </p>
<p><strong>Ski to the door location in the hamlet of Reberty, just above the centre of Les Menuires</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Ski from the door to the Sunny Express or Bruyeres lifts (100 metres)</li>
<li>Ten minutes' walk  to the centre of resort</li>
<li>Two minutes' walk (20 metres) to our partner ski hire shop</li>
</ul>
<p>The meeting place for our partner ski school (Prosneige) is at the Croisette. Walk 100 metres over to the blue Menuires piste and ski down, or there's a free bus that stops just outside and runs approximately every 15 minutes.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></locationDescription>
