  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard double room </strong>sleeps two people and are around 23m². These rooms have a large window with views of either the resort or mountains. Also available for sole occupancy, on request.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite </strong>sleeps two to three people and are around 37m². Made up of living area with a single sofa bed and a twin or double bedroom with balcony overlooking the mountains.</p>
<p><strong>Kaya Suite </strong>sleeps two adults &amp; two children and are around 46m². Made up of living room with views of the mountains, twin or double bedroom and an additional children's bedroom with bunk beds, suitable for children up to 12 years</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
